OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and mainly dry day,
OL,6,Fwith some sunny interludes. Still the
OL,7,Fchance of a few light showers, mainly
OL,8,Fover Shetland. Turning cloudy later in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain this
OL,12,Fevening will turn more persistent for
OL,13,Fa time in the early hours. Southerly
OL,14,Fwinds will fresh and become
OL,15,Foccasionally strong.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FEarly rain for Shetland, but
OL,18,Fmainly dry to start for Orkney.
OL,19,FThrough the day it will be bright but
OL,20,Frather cloudy with a few spots of rain
OL,21,Fat times. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
